The paper focuses on the accuracy of journal classification systems, which is a topic related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), social networks (cs.SI), and cybernetics (cs.CY). The in-depth analysis for the field of Library and Information Science also suggests a stronger connection to cs.DL.
